{"tid":1403064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好咁撚嘔心啦好無","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:09:30.000Z","uid":179616,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cf63505da9aea90375291f424bcaaf66720a86ad","tid":1403064,"uid":179616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"黑警已經公然咁想打擊記者同新聞自由 無論係精神上定肉體上<br />\n公然推跌記者 對正佢地射催淚彈<br />\n然後話我地絕對唔會攻擊記者「朋友」<br />\n唔好咁撚嘔心啦好無<br />\n「叫」佢地影下示威者 請問你地有咩權力命令記者做乜？<br />\n係咁用強光射佢地鏡頭<br />\n又話記者阻住佢地視線<br />\n搞到記者都差啲頂唔順同佢地起衝突 係咪要話埋記者暴動？<br />\n文宣可唔可以就呢個方向講下 為記者發下聲<br />\n已經由暗地裏唔妥記者去到浮晒面咁打壓新聞自由<br />\n<br />\nsource:啱啱黃大仙立場live"},{"pid":"0434cb82a237673b865d5e758c3494cfec685868","tid":1403064,"uid":283713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"推你上熱門"},{"pid":"21178c5e707b772dd48a0a0001019814b019da40","tid":1403064,"uid":122202,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"記者有晒立場扮乜野中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9478b4efa59995b2e0727cbd1320e492cfe1d1","tid":1403064,"uid":36478,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a7e09fad9d0942e9a136271ec9ff34665d6c4b","tid":1403064,"uid":21761,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"21178c5e707b772dd48a0a0001019814b019da40","tid":1403064,"uid":122202,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"記者有晒立場扮乜野中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"講緊文匯大公tvb呀傻閪?"},{"pid":"e80d36accb2401c47160955c8d074befffa30139","tid":1403064,"uid":62,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1c9478b4efa59995b2e0727cbd1320e492cfe1d1","tid":1403064,"uid":36478,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08